I entered the graphic design sector in 2019. I took a course around the middle of that year, but since it was just a basic course, I couldn't grasp how to establish myself in design for the long term. However, with just that basic knowledge, sustaining myself in the field for the long run wasn't feasible, so I ended up taking a break for quite a few years. 
Then, one day, I came across a detailed video on Facebook about Mithun Sarker's course. I started watching the videos he uploaded, and I was really impressed with his teaching style. Without a second thought, I decided to enroll. To those who are hesitant about joining, I want to say that you'll start seeing improvements very quickly. He provides 24-hour support to his students. Our course is still ongoing, and if you follow his guidance, you're bound to find work. However, income will come to those who can be patient and learn the skills properly first. 
Nowadays, thereтАЩs no shortage of people selling charms and amulets online, but instead of selling those, take Mithun SarkerтАЩs course to learn good design skills. ItтАЩs a Basic to Advanced course, so even complete beginners can join. YouтАЩll find an excellent mentor in him. Personally, I've received proper guidance in the graphic design sector through him. Thank you, Mithun Sarkar.
